#: admin/com_vikbooking:VBO_CRONJOB_INSTRUCTIONS_SCHEDTASKS
#, php-format
msgid "<p>Your Joomla! version allows you to automatically schedule the execution of the Cron Job you have set up. This configuration process does not require any additional set up on your own server by using the Control Panel, as it will be the Joomla framework itself to periodically execute your Cron Job. Follow the steps below to schedule the automatic execution of the Cron Job:</p><ol><li>Copy the execution URL for this Cron Job by using the input field below.</li><li>Visit the page to schedule a <a href=\\"%s\\" target=\\"_blank\\">new task %s</a> and click the &quot;New&quot; button.</li><li>Choose the <strong>GET Request</strong> task type from the list.</li><li>Paste the previously copied execution URL onto the field <strong>Request URL</strong> and set up the execution interval.</li><li>Save the new scheduled task within Joomla.</li><li>Click the button <strong>Run Task</strong> next to your newly created task to make a test.</li><li>Check the last execution time or the execution logs for your Cron Job within Vik Booking to make sure it was executed.</li></ol>That's all, Joomla will automatically and periodically execute your Cron Job!"
msgstr ""

