msgid "Percent %"
msgstr ""

#: site/mod_vikbooking_channelrates:VBOMODCMRCUSTRMODPCENTF
msgid "Absolute amount"
msgstr ""

#: site/mod_vikbooking_channelrates:VBOMODCMRCUSTRMODVAL
msgid "Custom increase value"
msgstr ""

#: site/mod_vikbooking_channelrates:VBOMODCMRCUSTRMODVALHELP
msgid "The value for increasing the website rates and to transmit them to the OTAs is taken automatically from what you have configured in Vik Channel Manager. However, you can force a custom increase value to be used for the calculation of the final costs for the OTAs by setting a value here greater than zero. Set the proper increase mode to use this value as a fixed or a percent amount."
msgstr ""

